---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import siteConfig from '@/site.config';
---

<Layout title="About - IC the Moon" enableFooterReveal={true}>
  <main class="page-content">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="hero-title">About IC the Moon</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Creating inclusive digital experiences through expert accessibility consulting</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="content-main">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>IC the Moon was founded with a simple mission: to make the digital world accessible to everyone. We believe that great design isn't just beautiful—it's inclusive, functional, and accessible to all users regardless of their abilities.</p>
            
            <h3>What We Do</h3>
            <p>We specialize in digital accessibility consulting, helping organizations create websites and applications that work for everyone. Our services include:</p>
            
            <ul>
              <li>Comprehensive accessibility audits</li>
              <li>WCAG compliance assessments</li>
              <li>User experience design with accessibility in mind</li>
              <li>Training and education for development teams</li>
              <li>Ongoing accessibility support and maintenance</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Our Approach</h3>
            <p>We don't just check boxes—we create meaningful, usable experiences. Every project starts with understanding your users and their needs, then we work to ensure your digital presence serves everyone effectively.</p>

            <blockquote>
              "Accessibility is not a feature to be added, but a fundamental aspect of good design."
            </blockquote>

            <h3>Why It Matters</h3>
            <p>Over 1 billion people worldwide live with some form of disability. When websites and applications are accessible, they're not only compliant with legal requirements—they're also more usable, discoverable, and profitable.</p>
          </div>
          
          <aside class="content-sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h4>Quick Facts</h4>
              <ul class="fact-list">
                <li><strong>Founded:</strong> 2023</li>
                <li><strong>Mission:</strong> Digital Inclusion</li>
                <li><strong>Focus:</strong> Accessibility & UX</li>
                <li><strong>Approach:</strong> User-Centered</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h4>Get In Touch</h4>
              <p>Ready to make your digital presence accessible to all?</p>
              <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
  }

  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 667px;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .content-main h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-main h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .content-main p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .content-main ul {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-main li {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  blockquote {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 10%, transparent);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--color-background);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 15%, transparent);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 8%, transparent);
  }

  .sidebar-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .fact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .fact-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 10%, transparent);
  }

  .fact-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .hero-section {
      padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>